  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK250">
<l>valiyārmuṟ ṟammai niṉaikkatān tammiṉ</l>
<l>meliyārmēṟ cellu miṭattu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When a man is about to rush upon those who are weaker than himself, let him remember how he has stood (trembling) before those who are stronger than himself.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
